Class StatPermCollectorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.md.statistics.manager.impl.StatPermCollectorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Runnable, StatPermCollector

    public class StatPermCollectorImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements StatPermCollector
    statistics-manager org.opendaylight.controller.md.statistics.manager.impl StatPermCollectorImpl Thread base statistic collector. Class holds internal map for all registered (means connected) nodes with List of Switch capabilities; Statistics collecting process get cross whole Network Device by device and statistic by statistic (follow Switch capabilities to prevent unnecessary ask) Next statistic start collecting by notification or by timeout.
    Author:
    @author avishnoi@in.ibm.com Vaclav Demcak
